review.practice_name: Sparsh- Orthopaedics and Sports Injury Centre
Sparsh- Orthopaedics and Sports Injury Centre

survey_response.review_text:
I visited the doc after 3 weeks of my injury. I accidently twisted my ankle and the pain was not reducing. Just withing 5 mins of explanation to the doc, he recommended to get an X-ray done as the pain was unberable. It was a hairline fracture and I got my leg casted for 3 weeks. After getting it removed, the pain completely subsided and I’m now able to walk as much as I want to. 
Dr. Amit is the friendliest doctor I have ever met. He also helps through texts and calls which is the most convenient way in today’s time. I definitely recommend Dr. Amit to the people reading this.

review.practice_name: Sparsh- Orthopaedics and Sports Injury Centre

survey_response.review_text:
I was suffering from achilles tendon tear in my ankle, met dr amit for it at sparsh hospital gurgaon.
He asked me to get mri done.
Mri clearly showed complete tear of my achilles tendon.
He adviced for surgery. Earlier i was mot happy with going for surgery but he convinced me explaining my illness in detail n why surgery was important.
Surgery went very well.
6 weeks later, m doing exercises well and i have started walking also.
Recovering well 🙏
Thank you Doctor saab for correct guidance

review.practice_name: Sparsh- Orthopaedics and Sports Injury Centre

survey_response.review_text: We met Doctor for spine injury wherein i had spinal fracture. He adviced us to undergo a minimally invasive surgery to avoid future complications. Initially we were a little hesitant, but he explained us pro and cons on detail. We even took a second opinion and ultimately we underwent surgery by dr amit. And m thankful that i listened to dr amits advice. Today i am back to normal self, started doing all my routine activities comfortably.. thank you doc 👍🙏🏻

review.practice_name: Sparsh- Orthopaedics and Sports Injury Centre

survey_response.review_text:
Got my humerus bone operated by Dr amit.
Surgery went good. 3 months later today, i am able to do all my activities which i did before my injury. Feels very good to get back to my life again. 
Would like to thank dr amit and his team for making sure everything goes smooth during my stay in th hospital.
Special mention to his friendly and caring nature. Made me feel like his family all the way

review.practice_name: Sparsh- Orthopaedics and Sports Injury Centre

survey_response.review_text:
Thank you Dr, Amit and team. Everyone was very friendly and I am grateful that you are in my nearby area. When you consult Amit sir, It's like dealing with a trusted family member.
He is a talented young orthopaedic surgeon in gurgaon. 
Diagnosed my cervical issue instantly. And started me on meds and physiotherapy and I am feeling much much better now. Able to work out which I badly wanted to resume. Very approachable.
Hes the go to man for any orthopedic problems.

review.practice_name: Sparsh- Orthopaedics and Sports Injury Centre

survey_response.review_text: We visited Doctor Amit for knee pain. Many doctors had adviced total knee replacement but my father was hesitant on getting it done at this age. Doctor understood our point and gave us alternative options of injections and physiotherapy that has worked wonders for my father till date. He has been doing his day to day activities comfortably now. Can't thank Dr Amit enough for this.
